{"tid":1463872,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"嘈完未呀 唔做都做左 再互屌 邊個最開心 自已諗下啦","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:07:27.000Z","uid":27485,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"838d8b2250035e4dc422913414ccf0a434288090","tid":1463872,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:56:40.000Z","msg":"覺得岩唔岩都好<br />\n講野好聽D 得唔得呀<br />\n自已人呀 洗唔洗講到人地一物不值<br />\n大家都係 同一個目標 咁嬲做乜鳩<br />\n要屌要鬧 都係屌政府屌黑警<br />\n唔係屌自已人呀<br />\n<br />\n再咁落去邊個最開心呀?<br />\n唔係你唔係我呀 <br />\n不割蓆不譴責不篤灰 講左2個幾月<br />\n係咪比班25狗搞一搞就完呀?<br />\n<br />\n依家邊個最鬼呀 就係開POST搵交嗌個班呀<br />\n就算比自已人屌完 都唔該冷靜下先 <br />\n我知你地都好嬲 但唔好再互屌啦!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不割蓆不譴責不篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不割蓆不譴責不篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不割蓆不譴責不篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不割蓆不譴責不篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不割蓆不譴責不篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6855f12da2d27fbe19fbd180776bc032aa1207d","tid":1463872,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:57:52.000Z","msg":"不割蓆不譴責不篤灰"},{"pid":"8300cf64576eb95b215dcd8e60affdde099f3fb9","tid":1463872,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:58:54.000Z","msg":"不割蓆不譴責不篤灰"},{"pid":"d8379ba8c93e1aa9a0bbefec72eae1a60881518f","tid":1463872,"uid":67479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不割蓆不譴責不篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj